[[Halloween Vendor]] is a year-round [[merchant]] that sells [[Halloween]]-themed items for [[Candy Corn]].

== Location ==
;[[Kryta]]
* [[Lion's Arch]]
** [[Hooligan's Route]]
*** [[The Undermarket]]

