== Notes ==
* Originally named Festival Rewards Vendor.
* The [[Game updates/2024-10-08|October 8, 2024 game update]] added to the inventory many items previously only available during the duration of the Halloween festival.

[[de:Händlerin für das Halloween-Fest]]
